 IROS 2018 Autonomous Drone Race\nCompetition, outracing the second-placing team by a factor of two.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Oct 2018 08:39:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Feb 2019 16:27:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 28 Feb 2019 15:48:31 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 1 Mar 2019 16:52:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-04"}
